text: Martti Maatela (born 21 September 1935) is a Finnish skier. He competed in the Nordic combined event at the 1960 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1935 births Category:Living people Category:Finnish male Nordic combined skiers Category:Olympic Nordic combined skiers of Finland Category:Nordic combined skiers at the 1960 Winter Olympics Category:People from Rovaniemi
